  <notes>For Conquer Online
----------------------
Has a custom window called "Potions" with 3 buttons (open from the Window menu).
Hover the pointer briefly over the "Start F6" button to start repeatedly pressing F6. 
Hover the pointer briefly over the "Start F7" button to start repeatedly pressing F7. 
Hover the pointer briefly over the "Stop F6 &amp; F7" button to stop the key presses. 

You only need to hover the pointer briefly over the buttons, no need to hold there or click.

The key presses are set to stop automatically after 5 seconds.</notes>
